OL,10,Fthe pseudonym AJ Finn, said he claimed
OL,11,Fto have had cancer as a way to disguise
OL,12,Fhis struggles with bipolar disorder.
OL,14,FHis admission comes after a New Yorker
OL,15,Fprofile accused him of a history of
OL,16,Flies about his personal life.
